Package: datacleaning
Title: A package for cleaning up the clusters of single-cell RNA-seq data
Type: Package
Version: 1.0
Author: F. M. Betul Erol
Maintainer: The package maintainer <fmab_erol@hotmail.com>
Description: datacleaning package provides functions for cleaning-up and visualizing the clusters of a SeuratObject generated from single-cell RNA-seq data. This package includes functions for cropping clusters, assigning cells to clusters based on their UMAP coordinates, and visualizing cluster assignments. 
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports:
    Seurat (>= 4.0),
    SeuratObject,
    ggplot2,
    rstatix,
    reshape2,
    dplyr,
    cowplot
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
    
